tional, but many have not honored their commitments.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/pcmc-developers-face-consequences-for-failing-to-supply-water-to-housing-societies/129889873?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-189480/129889873.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}